{"tid":1762224,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港政府新電視宣傳片　籲勿散播謠言","createTime":"2019-11-29T12:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T13:17:33.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1f7ff965e0a3130b0ad074bc9f9a28fc36fef5fa","tid":1762224,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T12:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20191129/s00001/24703027f50387cb7f2d20726b0af56b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20191129%2Fs00001%2F24703027f50387cb7f2d20726b0af56b.jpg&h=b434441b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府各部近期不時喺網上出「澄清」，要糾正一啲被指係造假嘅信息。繼早前搵政治助理拍短片，政府仲會推出新一輯電視宣傳短片，重點係叫大家唔好輕信網上信息，更提醒大家唔好將不實嘅消息散播出去，否則「後果可大可小」。不過，短片就無指明，邊啲消息係不實、邊啲人最鍾意散播謊言。<br />\n<br />\n宣傳短片提醒市民，喺網絡世界，每個人都可以發布信息，但唔係所有消息都真確，所以大家要從不同角度多了解，「核實過了才相信，不要讓情緒影響判斷」。"},{"pid":"2ac7c3d3af37f0369eeba643f02d00162478c0e3","tid":1762224,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T12:22:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191129/s00001/1575025870380/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191129%2Fs00001%2F1575025870380%2F&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=fe24c361\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191129%2Fs00001%2F1575025870380%2F&h=361c040d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191129/s00001/1575025870380/</a>"},{"pid":"c75f9348fc0948fec94109cbea146459accd43c2","tid":1762224,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T12:24:13.000Z","msg":"deadline fighter 一齊寫聖誕卡畀英國歐洲議員！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1761460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1761460</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n拉落去有哂英國address <br />\n依幾日截郵<br />\n幫手寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/d